Package: RCriteo
Type: Package
Title: RCriteo: Loading Criteo data into R
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-11-06
Author: Johannes Burkhardt <johannes.burkhardt@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Johannes Burkhardt <johannes.burkhardt@gmail.com>
Description: The aim of RCriteo is loading Criteo Campaign data into R. The
    package provides an authentication process for R with the Criteo API.
    Moreover, the package features an interface to query campaign data from the
    Criteo API. The data can be downloaded and will be transformed into a R
    data frame.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports:
    RCurl,
    XML,
    httr,
    plyr
License: GPL (>= 2) | MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jburkhardt/RCriteo
